							</listBibl>
							<explicit xml:lang="he">תם אבא אוריון<locus n="18v"/>
							</explicit>
							<incipit xml:lang="he">אבא אוריון פי' אסתר פי'<locus n="1r"/>
							</incipit>
						</msItem>
					</msContents>
					<physDesc rend="visible">
						<p>Parchment codex of approximately 13 or 14th century.</p>
						<objectDesc form="codex">
							<supportDesc material="perg">
								<support>Parchment codex. </support>
								<extent>18 folios<dimensions type="leaf" unit="mm">
										<height>120</height>
										<width>98</width>
									</dimensions>
									<dimensions type="written" unit="mm">
										<height>80</height>
										<width>62</width>
									</dimensions>
								</extent>
								<foliation>
									<p>18 folios (+2 modern paper flyleaves at the beginning and at the end).</p>
								</foliation>
								<collation>
									<p>2 quires of 8 leaves each and 2 additional folios at the beginning and at the end.</p>
									<p>Catchwords at the end of a quire.</p>
								</collation>
							</supportDesc>
							<layoutDesc>
								<layout columns="1" ruledLines="24 25" writtenLines="24 25">
									<p>Writing depends from the ruled line.</p>
									<p>Has a title page with a simple pen and ink design, folio <locus n="1r"/>.</p>
								</layout>
							</layoutDesc>
						</objectDesc>
						<handDesc hands="1">
							<summary/>
							<handNote script="Hebrew" scope="sole">
								<p>Sefardi semi-cursive script of approximately 13th or 14th century.</p>
							</handNote>
						</handDesc>
						<additions>
							<p>Folio 2r &amp; 2v is a modern paper. Contains a description of the manuscript in Latin.</p>
							<p>
								<name type="person" role="owner">Avraham ben Aharon</name>: inscribed, folio 1v.</p>
						</additions>
						<bindingDesc>
							<binding>
								<p>Post-1600. Light brown leather, blind-tooled.</p>
								<p>Spine title: 'Abba Urian. Comm. in Estheram. Mus. Brit. Jure Empt. 15,402. Plut.'</p>
								<p>Boxed.</p>
							</binding>
						</bindingDesc>
